titles.title: A bill to extend the existing suspension of duty on (6R,7R)-7-{(R)-2-Amino-phenylacetamido}-3-methyl-8-oxo-5-thia-1-azabicyclo{4.2.0}oct-2-ene-2-carboxylic acid disolvate.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 7/14/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend, through December 31, 1996, the suspension of duty on (6R, 7R)-7-((R)-2-amino-2-phenylacetamido)-3- methyl-8-oxo-5-thia-1-azabicyclo(4.2.0)oct-2-ene-2-carboxylic acid disolvate.
